## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **mRNA vaccine paradigm shift (2020-2021)** = COVID-19 era 의 가장 큰 vaccinology 진보. VIROCAPSID/RIBOZYME 본 axis 의 가장 명확 win.
2. **HIV vaccine 40-year challenge** — broadly neutralizing antibody discovery + epitope-stabilized immunogen design. quantum 직접 X (large-protein scope), 단 epitope rational design 가능.
3. **malaria 첫 FDA vaccine (Mosquirix 2021 / R21 2023)** = 30-year+ research 결과. partial protection (~30-50% efficacy).
4. **cancer neoantigen (BNT122 / mRNA-4157)** = personalized vaccine — cross-link cancer. quantum 의 epitope binding evaluation 가 future direction.
5. **adjuvant research crucial** — TLR9 (CpG) / STING / TLR4 (MPL) / etc 의 small-molecule 측 quantum-VQE 가능.
6. **vaccine hesitancy + access** = quantum-design 외부 issue, hexa-bio scope 한정.
7. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, vaccine 임상 의미 한정.

